#: ../../../source/How-To-Guides/Setup-ROS-2-with-VSCode-and-Docker-Container.rst:67
msgid ""
"Within VS Code search in Extensions (CTRL+SHIFT+X) for the \"Remote "
"Development\" Extension and install it."
